Package it.polimi.ingsw.events.clienttoserver

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    EventToServerNotifier
    This interface contains the list of methods that the client could use to send different events to the server.
    EventToServerVisitor
    This interface contains the list of the event that the server could receive form client.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    EventToServer
    This abstract class is used to generalize the event to sent from the client to the server.
    PingToServer
    This event represents the ping that verifies the connection with the server.
    ReplayLorenzoActionToServer
    This class represents the event to send to the server as reply of the LorenzoActionToClient.
    SelectedProductionToServer
    This class represents the event of the selection of the power production turn to send to the server .
    SendLeaderCardToServer
    This class represents the event to send to the server with the information of the leader card action choose by the player.
    TurnPlayedToServer
    This class represent the event send to the server for the choose of the type of turn.
